001package org.nasdanika.common;
002
003public class FilterConsumer<T> extends FilterExecutionParticipant<Consumer<T>> implements Consumer<T> { 
004
005        public FilterConsumer(Consumer<T> target) {
006                super(target);
007        }
008
009        @Override
010        public void execute(T arg, ProgressMonitor progressMonitor) {
011                target.execute(arg, progressMonitor);
012        }
013
014}
